,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"下 乜cctvb咁重要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b60b7ade26dba36db9100b5fbcdb0eb3988a9d","tid":660823,"uid":33651,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:45:19.000Z","msg":"出閃電十一人啦仆街"},{"pid":"529f3972175fe664a5e5608b18faf5ce30c581e4","tid":660823,"uid":161892,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"係 每次同朋友出街食飯 佢地成班拎晒switch出黎玩<br />\n我就自己一個匿埋一二邊玩手機 唔通帶部ps4出街玩咩😑"},{"pid":"e66bb32798c91adf0bba3c0bed3750691d7ad4f3","tid":660823,"uid":82889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86986eed7f4365f30c44e63be92346480c5db20a","tid":660823,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T01:52:33.000Z","msg":"對sony好撚失望"},{"pid":"24e25b9187abfcf780acc9ca2dcb0eaa849ee6ae","tid":660823,"uid":136354,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"98e089b81757a4b85ac0d357eb8f238ec2ee46f7","tid":660823,"uid":181330,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"fd2fe2f49c531149f21510accce95bd36801a883","tid":660823,"uid":121015,"like":20,"dislike":7,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"應該得心智未成熟既任豚，會將細路低B game當係寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"我身邊唔少人都向我反映過如果上既話佢地會出機，可惜一切已經無啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"其實講經係冇問題, 但你講經都要用下個腦, 諗一諗自己講既野.<br />\n<br />\nSONY PS4 已經賣出接近八千萬台. 所以你講乜野都係冇撚用, 人地已經食左半個MARKET. <br />\n<br />\n相反, 呢隻GAME 都係一D 食日本市場既野, PS4 唔係一部日本為主既主機, PS4 既以國際為主既, 你講咁多野, 對SONY 而言都只係小左果DD 日本市場, 你認為真係有好大影響嗎?<br />\n<br />\n再講返, 人地已經賣左咁多台, 你認為老任部SWITCH 真係比得到落去咩?<br />\n<br />\n人地成個PS4 CYCLE 都就完, 老任係人地尾期先出部SWITCH, 過兩年已經會出PS5, 到時SONY食住依家個方向係唔會怕有機賣唔出. <br />\n<br />\n因為PS4 起佢地唔會再換ARCHITECTURE, PS5 一定玩到PS4 既GAME, 而PS5 既GAME只要佢地出埋比PS4, PS4 係RUN 到. 最多要張個SETTING 拉低小小.<br />\n<br />\n而部SWITCH 有冇可能超越PS4 都係一個迷. <br />\n<br />\n睇野睇得一個小點, 比識野既人見到, 只會認為你ON 9. 學下放下有色眼鏡去睇事實啦.<br />\n事實, 呢一代CONSOLE WAR, SONY 係WINNER. <br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔係特別鐘意SONY, 都唔係對老任有咩好感, 只係DATA 上去講, 老任好難打得過人~"},{"pid":"be3daa0446bcd2a12188f3af66e309b0ab654c5f","tid":660823,"uid":180035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:47:03.000Z","msg":"其實有幾多人真係有玩開呢隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b5fac50441cad8175d4ef37c37914a1dde3f07","tid":660823,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"屌連係咩驚都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a408cd801670658d20671132e1fe82c590d64afb","tid":660823,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"哇 tvb 咁大影響力架原來"},{"pid":"0eaed12fc581f89bd672250609eaadc2c4bc83a6","tid":660823,"uid":60133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24e25b9187abfcf780acc9ca2dcb0eaa849ee6ae","tid":660823,"uid":136354,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"98e089b81757a4b85ac0d357eb8f238ec2ee46f7","tid":660823,"uid":181330,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"fd2fe2f49c531149f21510accce95bd36801a883","tid":660823,"uid":121015,"like":20,"dislike":7,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"應該得心智未成熟既任豚，會將細路低B game當係寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"我身邊唔少人都向我反映過如果上既話佢地會出機，可惜一切已經無啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"其實講經係冇問題, 但你講經都要用下個腦, 諗一諗自己講既野.<br />\n<br />\nSONY PS4 已經賣出接近八千萬台. 所以你講乜野都係冇撚用, 人地已經食左半個MARKET. <br />\n<br />\n相反, 呢隻GAME 都係一D 食日本市場既野, PS4 唔係一部日本為主既主機, PS4 既以國際為主既, 你講咁多野, 對SONY 而言都只係小左果DD 日本